<a href="/wiki/George_W._Bush" title="George W. Bush">President Bush</a> with with <a href="/wiki/A123Systems" title="A123Systems">A123Systems</a> <a href="/wiki/CEO" title="CEO" class="mw-redirect">CEO</a> on the <a href="/wiki/South_Lawn_(White_House)" title="South Lawn (White House)">White House South Lawn</a> examining a <a href="/wiki/Toyota_Prius" title="Toyota Prius">Toyota Prius</a> converted to plug-in hybrid with <a href="/wiki/Hymotion" title="Hymotion">Hymotion</a> technology.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Maker_Faire_2008_San_Mateo_154.JPG" class="image" title="Toyota Prius plug-in hybrid converted by CalCars with a fuel economy of over 100 miles per gallon."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bb/Maker_Faire_2008_San_Mateo_154.JPG/180px-Maker_Faire_2008_San_Mateo_154.JPG" width="180" height="120" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
